&lt;p&gt;UNIVERSITY HOSPITAL OF NORTH MIDLANDS NHS TRUST&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;COUNTY HOSPITAL&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;PORTERING &amp; SECURITY DEPARTMENT&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;VACANCY - Bank Portering &amp; Security officer&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;HOURS 0 hrs per week BANK&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;NUMBER OF POSTS X 3&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;RATE OF PAY Agenda for Change Band 2 &lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;We are currently looking to recruit an enthusiastic person to join our portering team who provide and maintain a professional, efficient, effective and timely service to patients, visitors and departments. Experience in this type of role is beneficial but is not essential as full training will be given.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Portering services are provided at the hospital 24 hours a day, 365 days a year, worked over various shifts including weekends. A flexible approach to work, smart appearance, good communication skills and a high standard of customer care is required.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;The positions will involve long periods of walking and moving bulky items from various parts of the hospital.&lt;/p&gt;
